hermes3d
========

Compilation
------------

$ cmake .
$ make

To customize the build, create CMake.vars file and set the appropriate variables.
Look into CMake.vars.example for more details.

Tests
-----

To run tests, do:

$ make test-quick

To run all tests (warning: takes very long time to finish):

$ make test

Debugging
---------

If you need to debug the build, use:

cmake -DCMAKE_VERBOSE_MAKEFILE=ON .

Then the make will print the exact commands that are executed.

